---
config:
  theme: base
  themeVariables:
    primaryColor: "#4A90D9"
    primaryTextColor: "#000"
    lineColor: "#555"
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant M as 上位机<br/>(Modbus 主站)
    participant S as STM32F407<br/>(Modbus 从站 0x01)

    Note over M,S: FC03 读保持寄存器

    M->>S: [01] [03] [00 10] [00 06] [CRC]<br/>读姿态 0x0010, 6个寄存器
    Note right of S: 查寄存器数组<br/>打包 12 字节数据
    S-->>M: [01] [03] [0C] [数据×12] [CRC]<br/>返回 6 个寄存器值 (3个float)
    Note left of M: regsToFloat()<br/>解析 IEEE754 浮点数

    Note over M,S: FC06 写单个寄存器

    M->>S: [01] [06] [00 20] [05 DC] [CRC]<br/>写 SERVO1 = 1500 (0x05DC)
    Note right of S: is_reg_writable? ✅<br/>apply_register()<br/>→ pwm_set_duty()
    S-->>M: [01] [06] [00 20] [05 DC] [CRC]<br/>回显确认 (Echo)

    Note over M,S: 写保护 — 写只读寄存器

    M->>S: [01] [06] [00 00] [FF FF] [CRC]<br/>尝试写 DEVICE_ID
    Note right of S: is_reg_writable? ❌
    S-->>M: [01] [86] [02] [CRC]<br/>异常响应 (Illegal Data Address)
